@base = http://localhost:{{port}}/api/third-addresses

### Crear dirección (residencia principal)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "thirdPartyId": 8,
  "addressType": "RESIDENCIA",
  "residenceZoneId": 5,
  "countryId": 19,
  "departmentId": 69,
  "municipalityId": 139,
  "address": "Calle 45 # 23-10",
  "neighborhood": "La Candelaria",
  "postalCode": "110111",
  "reference": "Frente al parque principal",
  "latitude": 4.7110,
  "longitude": -74.0721,
  "isPrincipal": true
}

###

### Crear dirección (correspondencia)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "thirdPartyId": 8,
  "addressType": "CORRESPONDENCIA",
  "countryId": 19,
  "departmentId": 69,
  "municipalityId": 139,
  "address": "Carrera 10 # 5-20 Apto 301",
  "isPrincipal": false
}

###

### Obtener dirección por ID
GET {{base}}/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar direcciones de un tercero
GET {{base}}/third/8
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Actualizar dirección
PUT {{base}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "residenceZoneId": 1,
  "countryId": 1,
  "departmentId": 1,
  "municipalityId": 1,
  "address": "Calle 45 # 23-10 Apto 201",
  "neighborhood": "La Candelaria",
  "postalCode": "110111",
  "reference": "Segundo piso",
  "latitude": 4.7110,
  "longitude": -74.0721,
  "isPrincipal": true
}

###

### Toggle activo/inactivo
PATCH {{base}}/1/toggle-active
Authorization: {{token}}
